    HttpHandler

    public class DefaultHttpHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements HttpHandler
    DefaultHttpHandler is an implementation of HttpHandler using OkHTTP. Customize this class for your own application by subclassing and overriding configureClient(OkHttpClient.Builder) and configureRequest(HttpUrl, Request.Builder).
